name: FOMO
description: FOMO is a community-powered memecoin on Avalanche, born in the fiery trenches of Avax. It captures the madness when FOMO hits different: tokens moon, bags pump, and timelines go full degen. In this PvE-style battleground, everyone’s winning. FOMO isn’t just a coin, it’s the banner of Avax culture, where missing out feels like a sin, ape season never ends, and diamond hands are forged in meme-fueled fire.
